  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6deeb46c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2icSMc1VBIYrDTprYP7HWKrgkzUCnqLehJKsbMiajPOuponnZwlIuXIvh6ojJFzVXLjFWYV0iaFBibmEDAnKiaApPrg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;color:inherit;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的都知道，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">Anthropic 对华的态度一直很不友好</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，但 Claude 在编程领域的素质确实独树一帜，因此很多的项目都会明着或暗着使用 Claude 模型（懂得都懂）</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247495789&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a3383f4655de75adf678abec522d5fea&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Anthropic CEO 发万字檄文：DeepSeek 崛起，白宫应加码管制\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Anthropic CEO 发万字檄文：DeepSeek 崛起，白宫应加码管制</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天早上，Anthropic 发布这么一则通告「</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-weight: bold;color: #1F2329 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">更新：对不受支持地区的销售限制</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">」</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 10px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021519\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3395522388059702\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1072\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width:100%;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;border:1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"576\" data-backh=\"772\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85abffcd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYrDTprYP7HWKrgkzUCnqLehs7s6mIH22URVSfelB2c3JzJ7C3cWPwsqV9AjYn4FxhbN7HtDciax3ibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以说，这是中美在 AI 对抗上的又一升级，要点如下：</span></span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style: none;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0;line-height: 2;padding-left: 0px;color: inherit;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 2;margin: 0;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-size:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(122, 163, 166, 1);margin-right: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-weight: bold;color: #1F2329 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">“股权穿透”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-weight: bold;color: #1F2329 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次限制是基于股权结构</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">，无论公司注册在新加坡、美国还是欧洲，只要是中国资方/人员控股 50%，都将被立即终止服务</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"font-size:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(122, 163, 166, 1);margin-right: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-weight: bold;color: #1F2329 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">政治明确</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Anthropic在公告中直接使用了“敌对国家 (adversarial nations)”等极具对抗性的词汇。</span></span></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">短期来看：</span></span><span style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">当前几家比较火热的 agent 项目，需要想好怎么应对技术、政治的双重考量了</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 0px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面原文，可以对应着来看</span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 10px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"709\" data-backw=\"351\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYrDTprYP7HWKrgkzUCnqLehzLnUKjhGl6nuRLqhg8ExmSbLZCADCJ5Fx8HTXacyVaBiavahiccSVQAw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"390.13888888888886\" data-cropx2=\"1689.375\" data-cropy1=\"1626.8055555555554\" data-cropy2=\"4251.041666666666\" data-imgfileid=\"100021520\" data-ratio=\"2.01875\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width:100%;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;border:1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=61f65ae8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2icSMc1VBIYrDTprYP7HWKrgkzUCnqLehlg7ZwFCicQqcrqiaAUiaeBapS8cb71BmFvk0JQEcomktGDB923Humvib0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 24px 0px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-weight: bold;color: inherit;font-size: 22px;line-height: 1.2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;color: #7AA3A6;font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-size: inherit;color: inherit;font-weight: bold;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 1.2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">题外话</span></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">配合来看，Claude 前两天发布了他们的融资新闻：</span><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic has completed a Series F fundraising of $13 billion led by ICONIQ. This financing values Anthropic at $183 billion post-money. Along with ICONIQ, the round was co-led by Fidelity Management &amp; Research Company and Lightspeed Venture Partners. The investment reflects Anthropic’s continued momentum and reinforces our position as the leading intelligence platform for enterprises, developers, and power users.</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">简单来说，就是 Anthropic 刚刚融了 130亿美金，由ICONIQ、Fidelity和Lightspeed领投，现在的估值是 1830 亿美金</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #666666;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;margin: 10px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">换句话说，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">Anthropic 现在的估值是 1830 亿美金</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">，相当于什么呢...</span></span></span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style: none;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0;line-height: 2;padding-left: 0px;color: inherit;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 2;margin: 0;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: #000000;margin-bottom: 2px;background-color: rgba(122, 163, 166, 1);margin-right: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">去年10月，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:12px;color:rgb(31, 35, 41) !important;word-break:break-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;min-height:20px;line-height:1.75;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">OpenAI估值为1570亿美元</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（OpenAI 现在的估值是约 3000～5000&nbsp;亿美金）</span></span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: #000000;margin-bottom: 2px;background-color: rgba(122, 163, 166, 1);margin-right: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7460856571062304770;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">根据公开融资数据，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（不算 DeepSeek）</span></span><sp